{"id": "1203115478189477938", "channel_id": "1203115478189477938", "type": 0, "author_id": "1176579168448823471", "author_name": "llhwwc_89248", "author_bot": false, "content": "昨天肝活动本没时间打，今天忙完试了一下，俩小时打完，体验还不错，就是要适应新压制环境，很多体系的思路需要灵活变化，潘狄娅不能all in一波，莉兹降低爆发持续上毒等等，同时需要配合好造物。\n\n按倒序打，54321。\n\n5图本来准备用达芙黛尔打的，然而凯刻斯确实不好处理。但是凯刻斯有个致命弱点是没有伤害成长且伤害频率低，打人也不疼，因此诺缔拉慢慢叠反击，温柯尔给诺缔拉续航，后期潘狄娅爆发，多拿持久战造物，拖死他即可。\n\n4图难度很大，需要对莉兹有比较深的理解，千万别被塞一手绿炎，那就纯等死了。前期交给操作，后期交给死抗。\n\n3图宁菲亚乱杀，我这队啥练度都没有，0启莉莉在毒队里依然很猛，1启艾尔瓦当个盾用，苟命就完事了，注射守护非常能苟。鼠鼠段数多，多拿衰竭。\n\n2图希洛一刀秒了.jpg，想办法活6回合拖过去锁血就行。\n\n1图纯乱杀不多说了，亏我还把巨人之刃、暴雨、致挚友、拉蒙娜留给深海队搭配，没想到这么不堪一击，早知道拿去给3队的混沌补强度了。\n\n这模式比深潜好玩多了，考察对队伍，命轮，造物，敌人的综合理解，非常有趣，喜欢，多出。\n\n祝大家早日30分毕业，欢迎评论区提问留言。\n\nPS：所有混沌角色除了罗坦全部用完了，嗯，但罗坦真不弱，昨天刚用四小强打了个万分。真完全玩不了的其实就凯刻斯和詹金，其它角色或多或少都能用，谨慎回退。", "timestamp": "2024-02-02T23:11:22.805000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-02-03T05:07:26.450000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 21}, {"emoji": "👋", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1203115478722027631", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-03-06-56-39-764_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 148279, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1203115478189477938/1203115478722027631/Screenshot_2024-02-03-06-56-39-764_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbabda&is=69ca5a5a&hm=15285d36ed773b9a8cbee444100c1473a4fbd57a2a1d1c0da8bb118962009ab1&"}, {"id": "1203115479066218586", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-03-06-56-38-029_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 142642, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1203115478189477938/1203115479066218586/Screenshot_2024-02-03-06-56-38-029_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbabdb&is=69ca5a5b&hm=74ad7836469c0c34df3a09de948601f2b29f31861197588ba08f31f7bfb61dfb&"}, {"id": "1203115479594438666", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-03-06-56-36-304_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 142869, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1203115478189477938/1203115479594438666/Screenshot_2024-02-03-06-56-36-304_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbabdb&is=69ca5a5b&hm=0496a5b799bb5c12507309bfef7e98def5561346198087b2b8daeb82cfb9318f&"}, {"id": "1203115480097882222", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-03-06-56-34-364_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 140131, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1203115478189477938/1203115480097882222/Screenshot_2024-02-03-06-56-34-364_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbabdb&is=69ca5a5b&hm=2587b14a946008872a34ac6a4bc1e7a4b6d1b7cfc61b7c6f639675d6ab6d861c&"}, {"id": "1203115480412463114", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-03-06-56-31-425_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 138279, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1203115478189477938/1203115480412463114/Screenshot_2024-02-03-06-56-31-425_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbabdb&is=69ca5a5b&hm=162270934432081924f7c360c2f5a12501223b53a50565a000f674e9c4c8e620&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203115478189477938", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融灾已满分，作业已出", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
